Package stars

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FlatFileObject
    An interface implemented by objects that can be written to and read from files in flat file format.
    StarsNotifier
    Interface implemented by notification service provider classes used in the MySTARS program system.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminProgram
    A class that represents the program a admin will use when accessing MySTARS.
    Course
    Class that represents a course that a student can register for during add/drop period.
    CourseDatabase
    A class that reads from and writes to a file containing course information in flat file format and stores them in memory for access.
    CourseManager
    A class that manages the data of of courses and indexes within the STARS system.
    FlatFileDatabase<T extends FlatFileObject>
    A class that reads, stores and write data from from to a flat file.
    Index_details
    A class that represents a course index that a student can register for during add/drop period.
    IndexClass
    Class representing a lesson under a course and containing its details.
    IndexDatabase
    Database class that implements FlatFileDatabase that handles stores and handles Index_details objects.
    MySTARS  
    PasswordModule
    Class for generating hashes from plaintext passwords and verifying them.
    StarsDatabase
    A class that serves as intermediary between the databases that contains user and student information, and programs that access the data in those databases.
    StarsMail
    Implementation of StarsNotifier that provides functionality of sending email through the MySTARS system.
    Student_details
    A class that holds the details regarding a student who uses the Stars system.
    StudentDatabase
    Database class that implements FlatFileDatabase that handles stores and handles Student_details objects.
    StudentProgram
    A class that represents the program that a student will use during add/drop period.
    User_details
    A class that holds details regarding a user's account A user can be either a student or an admin.
    UserDatabase
    Database class that implements FlatFileDatabase that handles stores and handles User_details objects.
  • Enum Summary

    Enum of the typesof classes possible under a course.
    StarsNotificationType
